<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Residents.27_resistance_to_use_of_DDT"><span class="tocnumber">5.3</span> <span class="toctext">Residents' resistance to use of DDT</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Human_exposure_associated_with_DDT_spraying_for_disease_vectors"><span class="tocnumber">5.4</span> <span class="toctext">Human exposure associated with DDT spraying for disease vectors</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Criticism_of_restrictions_on_DDT_use"><span class="tocnumber">5.5</span> <span class="toctext">Criticism of restrictions on DDT use</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Alternatives_to_DDT"><span class="tocnumber">5.6</span> <span class="toctext">Alternatives to DDT</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#DDT_versus_other_insecticides"><span class="tocnumber">5.6.1</span> <span class="toctext">DDT versus other insecticides</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#DDT_versus_non-chemical_vector_control"><span class="tocnumber">5.6.2</span> <span class="toctext">DDT versus non-chemical vector control</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">6</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
