<li id="cite_note-115"><b><a href="#cite_ref-115" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCorin.2C_S._E_.26_Weaver.2C_S.A.2005">Corin, S. E &amp; Weaver, S.A. (2005). "<a href="http://www.jcu.edu.au/jrtph/vol/v04corin.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.jcu.edu.au/jrtph/vol/v04corin.pdf" rel="nofollow">A risk analysis model with an ecological perspective on DDT and malaria control in South Africa</a>" (PDF). <i>Journal of Rural and Tropical Public Health</i> <b>4</b>: 21–32. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1046%2Fj.1365-3156.2001.00700.x" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1046%2Fj.1365-3156.2001.00700.x" rel="nofollow">10.1046/j.1365-3156.2001.00700.x</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.jcu.edu.au/jrtph/vol/v04corin.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.jcu.edu.au/jrtph/vol/v04corin.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.jcu.edu.au/jrtph/vol/v04corin.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=A+risk+analysis+model+with+an+ecological+perspective+on+DDT+and+malaria+control+in+South+Africa&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Rural+and+Tropical+Public+Health&amp;rft.aulast=Corin%2C+S.+E+%26+Weaver%2C+S.A.&amp;rft.au=Corin%2C+S.+E+%26+Weaver%2C+S.A.&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.volume=4&amp;rft.pages=21%E2%80%9332&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1046%2Fj.1365-3156.2001.00700.x&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jcu.edu.au%2Fjrtph%2Fvol%2Fv04corin.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:DDT"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
